// E2E tests for :help Erlang <module> (BT-1852)
//
// Tests FFI documentation lookup combining type specs and EEP-48 docs.

// :help Erlang with a known module — should show module header, docs, and functions
:help Erlang lists
// => Erlang module: lists_

// :help Erlang with a specific function — should show type signature and docs
:help Erlang lists reverse
// => lists:reverse_

// :help Erlang with a nonexistent module — should show error
:help Erlang nonexistent_module_xyz
// => ERROR: Erlang module 'nonexistent_module_xyz' not found

// :help Erlang with a nonexistent function — should show error
:help Erlang lists nonexistent_function_xyz
// => ERROR: lists:nonexistent_function_xyz not found

// :help Erlang with no module name — shows the Erlang class docs
:help Erlang
// => == Erlang < ProtoObject ==_

// :help Erlang maps — another common module should work
:help Erlang maps
// => Erlang module: maps_
